<plot>Played by filmmaker Michal Bet-Adam, Aya is a woman who, since early childhood, has been driven by her father's ambition to see her become successful. She wants to achieve something worthwhile so that her father can be proud of her. She is shooting a film--fragments of dreams and fantasy that alternate with real or imagined realities.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?051922</url></doc>
